com.rscja.deviceapi.interfaces

Interface IReader

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBluetoothReader, IRFIDWithUHFUSB, IUhfBle, IUhfReader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BluetoothReader, BluetoothReader_qcom, EmptyUhfBle, RFIDWithUHFBLE, RFIDWithUHFBLE_qcom, RFIDWithUHFBLEN51_qcom, RFIDWithUHFBLEN52_qcom, RFIDWithUHFUSB, RFIDWithUHFUSB_qcom, UHFTemperatureTag, UHFTemperatureTag.RFIDWithUHFBLEN51, UHFTemperatureTag.RFIDWithUHFBLEN52, UHFTemperatureTagsBLEAPI

    public interface IReader
    R2、R5、R6 蓝牙和USB读写器 有些客户只需要我们R6的背夹，不需要uhf模块，所以将R6背夹接口独立出来
    Author:
    zhoupin
